{"tid":1837051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"算閪數啦，你班港豬敢撚唔返工咩？","createTime":"2020-01-23T12:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T00:37:53.000Z","uid":240250,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1bd7d58b9df0e7f2fc69f1ed9b47a67826b91326","tid":1837051,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:30:55.000Z","msg":"講撚左半年都未罷，你班垃圾一早露撚哂底牌啦，就算肺炎大爆發睇死你哋咪又係戴個口罩準時返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f30356cfb162fe45ad3ecce1b8c2f6192fff7f","tid":1837051,"uid":198590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:31:12.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#240250 - 徐永強</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>我正式宣布，大家休息至立法會選舉！！！ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>前線手足嘅血汗總算有回報，大家記住沉著冷靜，唔好再開花，免得令民意逆轉！記住血債票償呀！要喺體制內打贏佢哋！<br />\n嚟！一齊叫！光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1756452/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1756452/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>香港人終於贏左第一仗！多謝勇武手足，你地終於可以退下火線 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>首先多謝各位前線勇武手足，你地嘅血汗已經化為選票，我哋幫你報咗仇。<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fhoho.gif&h=26011529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n區選大勝，證明民意喺我哋呢邊，我哋下一步就係要建立黃色經濟圈，<br />\n等啲黃店發大嚟搞，請返留咗案底嘅手足，再下一步就係贏埋立法會選舉。<br />\n現階段抗爭運動正式轉形，最緊要唔好再搞以下幾樣野，<br />\n因為太影響民生或者畫面唔好睇，有可能會令民意反彈：<br />\n1. 堵路<br />\n2. 火魔<br />\n3. 裝修<br />\n4. 神獸<br />\n5. 黎明行動<br />\n6. 三罷<br />\n想繼續表達訴求嘅可以考慮星期日搞下遊行集會（記得要有不反），<br />\n記住唔好影響市民，唔好失民意，最好做咗都冇人知！<br />\nCome on！光復香港！時代革命！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" />[img]<a href=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gi&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeP5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=29f79c50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi</a></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1755038/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1755038/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>運動已完，大家請接受現實 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>打左幾個月而家先返轉頭玩和理非玩感化，一定冇noise。林鄭嘅策略簡單暴力，但非常成功地將前線拉得七七八八，剩返嗰班和理非不足為患（其實對家由頭到尾都冇放和理非在眼內），就由得你喺度圍爐打飛機，打多排冇癮就自己散。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1743386/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1743386/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>請立即停止黎明行動！ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>黎明左咁多日，打工仔都適應哂，要返工嘅早兩個鐘出門口爬山都會返工，最多係遲一兩個鐘，但再搞落去只會令打工仔屌聲四起，增加民鬥民嘅情況。我呼籲大家立即停止黎明行動，準時返工返學方為上策。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1740561/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1740561/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>正式宣布黎明行動唔撚使再搞 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>好簡單既道理：一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭。<br />\n所有招數都係用一次，唔食住上星期個勢搞落去就唔使旨意再搞，你不妨睇下呢場運動有咩招數係停完之後再攞返出黎用係work既？<br />\n所以各位準時返工啦<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fsmile.gif&h=d434394b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1737015/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1737015/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/4Re5r6q.png\" />"},{"pid":"2904afd8b33ab9f2a580a3f5b3ec4dd2d4a56e66","tid":1837051,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:34:18.000Z","msg":"屌你地老母"},{"pid":"2ef390fd4cb0c08c1ebfe4b5b01a69dcba5ea9f3","tid":1837051,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135a1d9ae6f79a5bf6e0567c737bef364d01eddc","tid":1837051,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:34:19.000Z","msg":"夠鐘返工喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee78db41546cb57212a7b9247855ff6523a3b51","tid":1837051,"uid":235764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bd7d58b9df0e7f2fc69f1ed9b47a67826b91326","tid":1837051,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:30:55.000Z","msg":"講撚左半年都未罷，你班垃圾一早露撚哂底牌啦，就算肺炎大爆發睇死你哋咪又係戴個口罩準時返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:37:53.000Z","msg":"請睇2樓留言及起底"}]}